🛠️ Project Structure
suricata-idps/
├── rules/                # Suricata rules (custom and example rules)
├── scripts/              # Automation scripts for installation and management
├── webapp/               # Web application files for monitoring logs
│   ├── index.html        # Main web page
│   ├── styles.css        # CSS for styling
│   ├── app.py            # Backend logic for the web app
│   ├── logs/             # Directory for log files (fast.log, error.log)
├── configs/              # Configuration files (suricata.yaml, etc.)
├── README.md             # Project documentation
├── LICENSE               # License file (e.g., MIT License)
└── setup.md              # Detailed setup instructions
